snippet.title: Chisholm Trail Texas Instruments 99 TI-99 game
snippet.description:
Video of Chisholm Trail game on the Texas Instruments 99 (TI-99) computer. I'm not sure what the objective of the game is other than killing those "stompy" things. 

You have limited shots (50) and random laser beams coming out of those spouts at the edges of the screen. Similar to Munch man later levels start introducing new (colourful?) sprites for enemies.
